        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"657719\">Terence Tao</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/423402-PrimeNumberTheorem.2B/topic/Fej.C3.A9r's.20theorem.20has.20just.20been.20formalized/near/569618453\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Would you like to upload it to PNT+ (in a Mathlib subdirectory, perhaps) to help with other number theory formalizations?  </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>With pleasure - newbie question:  how and where do I upload?</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Or is the plan to send it directly to Mathlib? I guess it would need a lot of golfing first.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Exactly - yes, but not right away; I was hoping we would golf communally - and, as a result, I'd learn to golf (or at least I'd learn more Lean).</p>\n<p>It apparently failed to upload last night - here it is.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/eMJl007Vv1xdbhCkYWR0120q/Fejer-verbatim-building-on-DJstep1-step-2.lean\">Fejer verbatim building on DJstep1, step 2.lean</a></p>",
